{"tid":1799181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【實戰】【要改善】請不要同狗隻合照","createTime":"2019-12-26T18:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T07:00:57.000Z","uid":253691,"like":68,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"16476ce5d62f5b69693ec9216fa4f5305be7d65d","tid":1799181,"uid":253691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:20:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">tl;dr </span></span><br />\n3 隻字：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">損己利人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原因：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">1) 對己方無任何幫助</span></span><br />\n大叫「你老婆畀狗屌」，唱「人又廢，又要威」都有起馬谷到己方士氣，引狗犯錯；但同狗影相除左喺 facebook / twitter 打飛機之外，<span style=\"color: red;\">跟本無任何幫助，連文宣 / 集氣都唔係</span>。<br />\n<br />\n此風不可長<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">2) 狗隻只會增強士氣</span></span><br />\n狗隻係低智生物，除左中指之外，唔會識睇你做咩 5 1 手勢，見到咁多人去同佢影相，以為自己好多 fans，<span style=\"color: red;\">只會增強信心</span>。<br />\n<br />\n明明大家屌狗屌幾個月，屌撚到佢士氣勁低，人見人憎，而家做乜幫佢地集氣？<br />\n<br />\n例子（狗樣幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QAg0yFS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQAg0yFS.jpg&h=877c387c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRef: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PokeguideHK/photos/a.1623490984582016/2429074704023636/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPokeguideHK%2Fphotos%2Fa.1623490984582016%2F2429074704023636%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=8aebfdad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PokeguideHK/photos/a.1623490984582016/2429074704023636/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">3) 狗隻好易做文宣材料</span></span><br />\n好多市民同狗隻影相，大肆宣揚<span style=\"color: red;\">得到市民支持，狗民關係改善</span> (你做 5 1 手勢之前，總有一刻正正常常，就拎住呢一張相 / 呢一秒片段)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">4) 自爆起底</span></span><br />\n個樣直接曝光，狗唔巢你出黎，大陸都巢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d882acc77646bb3cc94295644b2b18ebb98fbe9","tid":1799181,"uid":214453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:26:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79f62f481aa78082f26661bb370a0e953be96888","tid":1799181,"uid":214453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:26:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a205b85556480c6038d6cb6d75d4bb237a9bfa8c","tid":1799181,"uid":203799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:26:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd9c8b110f4d9f01eb5524e60802c47311976dec","tid":1799181,"uid":214453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:26:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a713e261b032ee32a402b3ce2683a964daeaf71","tid":1799181,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:27:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92a0dc3729ad8238831a5c6c0c5b5123a998ec17","tid":1799181,"uid":16676,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:28:22.000Z","msg":"聽朝國難會出黎講架喇<br />\n然後會話停3日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f458574455706cd7dea5a4902a603da3b654745","tid":1799181,"uid":207093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:28:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04e5ff9bfb0b4999b7597d48d81686202523b247","tid":1799181,"uid":286309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:30:07.000Z","msg":"下不為例做左就算，的確要檢討下"},{"pid":"909958ed9219409700ac98ff138a655fe118b338","tid":1799181,"uid":8600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:30:31.000Z","msg":"第4點我諗英領&quot;被叫雞&quot;果位都講得好清楚被認出＋自行送中會有咩後果<br />\n以大陸BIG DATA加埋人面識別基本上係網絡上由其媒體留過樣都好難再番強國<br />\nBTW想屌我係隔離個POST爆人樣既麻煩唔好咁天真覺得一個普通人手頭上資料會比中共多而且我唔係第一手。"},{"pid":"abc08b81f883a8ccd5d86b5a49fc39eedb2464eb","tid":1799181,"uid":38692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:40:15.000Z","msg":"玩撚夠未<br />\n抗爭可唔可以嚴肅啲"},{"pid":"7aab7e66856fd203627576a4ecf75cc230550fa4","tid":1799181,"uid":210140,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"abc08b81f883a8ccd5d86b5a49fc39eedb2464eb","tid":1799181,"uid":38692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:40:15.000Z","msg":"玩撚夠未<br />\n抗爭可唔可以嚴肅啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:41:15.000Z","msg":"因住俾人話分化，兄弟爬山<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e95dad6c234fb5dda60a5515dd4403908b2214","tid":1799181,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:41:27.000Z","msg":"On9 琴日個後生仔post <br />\n幾多正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bba376198ea9e73c2e4e0a0479caebe07027d2","tid":1799181,"uid":341811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T19:07:49.000Z","msg":"以前有冇影相都算啦<br />\n總之依家大家明呢種撚狗方式係膠且無成效仲要危險<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>要改善啊各位</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>要贏就要有進步 咪再犯同樣嘅錯</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25e74035fcfaab369db0977360afa731929df87","tid":1799181,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T19:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8255137b65944061bba30d62ae7d725